            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>Release Date: May 6, 2008 [EBook #25352]\nLast updated: September 25, 2013</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>Language: Chinese</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK CHANG HEN GE YAN JIU ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Huang Xiang-Ru</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">長恨歌    白居易</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>漢皇重色思傾國，御宇多年求不得，楊家有女初長成，養在深閨人未識。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>天生麗質難自棄，一朝選在君王側，回眸一笑百媚生，六宮粉黛無顏色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>春寒賜浴華清池，溫泉水滑洗凝脂，侍兒扶起嬌無力，始是新承恩澤時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>雲鬢花顏金步搖，芙蓉帳暖度春宵，春宵苦短日高起，從此君王不早朝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>承歡侍宴無閒暇，春從春遊夜專夜，後宮佳麗三千人，三千寵愛在一身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>金屋妝成嬌侍夜，玉樓宴罷醉和春，姊妹弟兄皆列土，可憐光彩生門戶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>遂令天下父母心，不重生男重生女，驪宮高處入青雲，仙樂風飄處處聞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>緩歌謾舞凝絲竹，盡日君王看不足，漁陽鞞鼓動地來，驚破霓裳羽衣曲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>九重城闕煙塵生，千乘萬騎西南行，翠華搖搖行復止，西出都門百餘里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>六軍不發無奈何，宛轉蛾眉眼前死，花鈿委地無人收，翠翹金雀玉搔頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>君王掩面救不得，回看血淚相和流，黃埃散漫風蕭索，雲棧縈紓登劍閣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>峨眉山下少人行，旌旗無光日色薄，蜀江水碧蜀山青，聖主朝朝暮暮情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>行宮見月傷心色，夜雨聞鈴腸斷聲，天旋地轉迴龍馭，到此躊躇不能去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>馬嵬坡下泥土中，不見玉顏空死處，君臣相顧盡霑衣，東望都門信馬歸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>歸來池苑皆依舊，太液芙蓉未央柳，芙蓉如面柳如眉，對此如何不垂淚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>春風桃李花開日，秋雨梧朿落葉時，西宮南內多秋草，落葉滿階紅不掃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>梨園子弟白髮新，椒房阿監青娥老，夕殿螢飛思悄然，孤燈挑盡未成眠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>遲遲鐘鼓初長夜，耿耿星河欲曙天，鴛鴦瓦冷霜華重，翡翠衾寒誰與共。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>悠悠生死別經年，魂魄不曾來入夢，臨邛道士鴻都客，能以精誠致魂魄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>為感君王輾轉思，遂教方士覓殷勤，排氣馭雲奔如電，升天入地求之遍。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>上窮碧落下黃泉，兩處茫茫皆不見，忽聞海山有仙山，山在虛無飄渺間。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>樓閣玲瓏五雲壺，其中綽約多仙子，中有一人字太真，雪膚花貌參差是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>金闕西廂叩玉局，轉教小玉報雙成，聞道漢家天子使，九華帳裡夢驚魂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>攬衣推枕起徘徊，珠箔銀屏迤邐開，雲髻半偏新睡覺，花冠不整下堂來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>風吹仙袂飄飄舉，猶似霓裳羽衣舞，玉容寂寞淚闌干，梨其一枝春帶雨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>含情凝睇謝君王，一別音容兩渺茫，昭陽殿裡恩愛絕，蓬萊宮中日月長。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>回頭下望塵寰處，不見長安見塵霧，惟將舊物表深情，鈿合金釵寄將去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>釵留一股合一扇，釵擘黃金合分鈿，但教心似金鈿堅，天上人間會相見。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>臨別殷勤重寄辭，詞中有誓兩心知，七月七日長生殿，夜半無人私語時。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>在天願作比翼鳥，在地願為連理枝，天長地久有時盡，此恨綿綿無絕期。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of Chang Hen Ge Yan Jiu, by Bai Juyi</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/badf4659084214c9/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>*** END OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK CHANG HEN GE YAN JIU ***</p></div>"
        },
