            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-badf4659084214c9-f09fcd twpub-badf4659084214c9-6b4cd0\"><p>***** This file should be named 25352-0.txt or 25352-0.zip *****\nThis and all associated files of various formats will be found in:\n        http://www.gutenberg.org/2/5/3/5/25352/</p></div>"
        },
